    %p
      %a.inline-link{:href => "https://goo.gl/maps/Z8Sa4T6sb3n"} 133-135 Bethnal Green Road
      •
      %a.inline-link{:href => "mailto:contact@newspeak.house"} contact@newspeak.house
      •
      %a.inline-link{:href => "https://twitter.com/nwspk"} @nwspk

    %h2 Your Visit
    %p
      Our Newspeak House campus is located in London at the intersection of Brick Lane and Bethnal Green Road. The nearest underground station is Shoreditch High Street. The full address is:%br/Newspeak House%br/133-135 Bethnal Green Road%br/London%br/England%br/E2 7DG

    %h3 Accessibility
    %p
      The downstairs event space is wheelchair accessible without steps however please let us know if you need a ramp. This floor has an accessible bathroom with extra support. The upstairs space is accessed by two flights of stairs with rails. This is not a scent free space. 
    %p
      We are always looking to improve, so if there are any accessibility needs that you think we could accommodate but don’t currently, please contact
      %a.inline-link{:href => "mailto:contact@newspeak.house"}> &nbsp;contact@newspeak.house
    
    %h3 Parking
    %p
      Bethnal Green Road has on-street paid parking:
    %table{:border => "0",:padding => "5px"}
      %tr
        %td Mon-Fri
        %td 08:30 - 17:30
      %tr
        %td Saturday
        %td Free all day
      %tr
        %td Sunday
        %td 08:30 - 14:30
    %p
      Max stay 4 hours, no return within 2 hours. Pay via 
      %a.inline-link{:href => "https://ringgo.co.uk"} ringgo.co.uk
      or phone 0203 046 0010 and quote location number 60221 (Bethnal Green Road).
    
    
